window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The first volume of the extraordinary Southern Reach trilogy - now a major motion picture written and directed by Alex Garland (<i>Ex Machina</i>) and starring Natalie Portman and Oscar Isaac.</b> </p> <p>For thirty years, Area X has remained mysterious and remote behind its intangible border â€“ an environmental disaster zone, though to all appearances an abundant wilderness. The Southern Reach, a secretive government agency, has sent eleven expeditions to investigate Area X. One has ended in mass suicide, another in a hail of gunfire, the eleventh in a fatal cancer epidemic. Now four women embark on the twelfth expedition into the unknown. </p>"; 
